const pieceCodes= { 
  Pawn: 1,
  Knight: 2,
  Bishop: 3,
  Rook: 4,
  Queen: 5,
  King: 6,
  White: 0,
  Black: 8,
  White: 16,
  None: 0,

}

const pieces = {
  p: pieceCodes.Pawn | pieceCodes.Black,
  n: pieceCodes.Knight | pieceCodes.Black,
  b: pieceCodes.Bishop | pieceCodes.Black,
  r: pieceCodes.Rook | pieceCodes.Black,
  q: pieceCodes.Queen | pieceCodes.Black,
  k: pieceCodes.King | pieceCodes.Black,
  P: pieceCodes.Pawn | pieceCodes.White,
  N: pieceCodes.Knight | pieceCodes.White,
  B: pieceCodes.Bishop | pieceCodes.White,
  R: pieceCodes.Rook | pieceCodes.White,
  Q: pieceCodes.Queen | pieceCodes.White,
  K: pieceCodes.King | pieceCodes.White,
};

export default pieces;
